(11, NULL, 'saya-tidak-dapat-menggunakan-kupon', 'Saya tidak dapat menggunakan kupon', '<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-left: 36pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Sebelum menggunakan kupon, terdapat beberapa hal yang perlu kamu perhatikan yaitu:</span></p>\r\n<ol style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\">\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 36pt;\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Syarat dan ketentuan kupon</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-left: 72pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Pastikan produk kamu cocok dengan syarat dan ketentuan yang tertera</span></p>\r\n<ol style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\" start=\"2\">\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 36pt;\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Batas penggunaan kupon</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-left: 72pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Pada setiap kupon terdapat batas penguaan yang berbeda</span></p>\r\n<ol style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\" start=\"3\">\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: decimal; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre; margin-left: 36pt;\">\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Cek masa penggunaan kupon</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.38; margin-left: 72pt; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Pastikan masa penggunaan kupon yang ingin anda gunakan masih dalam waktu promo</span></p>