d-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Selanjutnya, klik </span><span style=\"font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Batalkan Pesanan</span></p>\r\n</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n<p><span id=\"docs-internal-guid-9c78801a-7fff-b4f2-f1b1-d956d7efdc0a\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0; padding-inline-start: 48px;\">\r\n<li dir=\"ltr\" style=\"list-style-type: disc; font-size: 11pt; font-family: Arial; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: 400; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre;\"></li>\r\n</ul>', 4, '2021-08-13 02:58:58', '2021-08-13 02:58:58');